       BEFORE RUNNING!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!    |
-----------------------------------------

Edit pools.txt with notepad or any text editor.
----------------------------------------------------------------------

this is an example on how to connect to the minegeeks monero pool
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
"pool_list": [
    {
        "pool_address": "xmr.minegeeks.com:5555",
        "wallet_address": "your_wallet_address",
        "rig_id": "worker_name",(will identify your miner)(use any name)
        "pool_password": "x",(do not change)
        "use_nicehash": false,
        "use_tls": false, /* Set to true if you are using an SSL port */
        "tls_fingerprint": "",
        "pool_weight": 1
    },
],
"currency": "cryptonight_v7",
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^


run xmr-stak exectuable
